{
  "texts": [
    "The MARC dataset comprises a multilingual assemblage designed for the categorization of Amazon product reviews.",
    "Product reviews are presented in multiple languages, including English, Japanese, German, French, Chinese, and Spanish.",
    "Each specific instance includes a review, star rating, and broad product category, covering classifications like \"books\" and \"home appliances.\"",
    "• THUCNews foot_82.",
    "The THUCNews dataset originates from the curated historical data of Sina Weibo's subscription channels between 2005 and 2011."
  ]
}